Image Prompt:
Create a serene and majestic landscape depicting a lush garden with abundant fruits and blooming flowers, under a radiant sun. In the center of the garden, depict a pair of hands gently cradling and nurturing the plants, symbolizing God as the sustainer of life. Rays of light should be shining down from above, illuminating the scene with a divine glow. Let the image evoke a sense of peace, harmony, and the nurturing presence of God as the ultimate sustainer of all creation.
